  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees.",
    "Char the peppers by placing them on a baking sheet and roasting for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the peppers from the oven and let them cool.",
    "Peel the peppers and chop them into large pieces.",
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and garlic to the pot and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper to the pot and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the chopped peppers, canned tomatoes, and white fish to the pot and stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes or until the fish is cooked through."
